{
  "stem": "1415.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she beat her to death, they took her away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was quite a few, quite a few.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it was always something that wasn't pleasing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she just wanted-- I felt she wanted to show for the Germans that she was efficient and she was doing her job.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or her anger, the fact that she's been there all this time, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was a young woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Looking back, maybe in her late 20s, early 30s, middle 30s, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But this went on day in and day out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we would periodically go to the bathroom as a group, and the bathroom was one barrack made out of holes, you know, whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] She asked me to go to the head of the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But just before that, we went through another scrubbing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, going to the showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I must have stood a little longer at the shower, because when I got through, all I got is a shirt.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All they were able to give me was a shirt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother got a slip, because she was waiting for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she got a slip, like a cotton slip or something, and I got a shirt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "No underwear, no nothing, just a shirt for my mother-- um, for me, and a slip for my mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the block-- when the-- when I went to hear the block eldester, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all I had is that shirt.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was wearing it like Tarzan, around my middle, and I tied the sleeve behind me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was Tarzan, the woman of apes or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to sing.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
